quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  85,1,"lbut ko Langit, a katatagowan sa manga darpa o manga Bito-on,"
  85,2,"Go so Alongan a di diyandi-in (a so Alongan a Qiyamah),"
  85,3,"Go so saksi, a go so pushaksi­an;"
  85,4,"Pimorka-an so khimangaruk ko kakar,"
  85,5,"A Apoi a tatagowan sa itagon,"
  85,6,"Gowani a siran na Mo-ontod siran ko obai niyan,"
  85,7,"A siran na mbabantayan niran so ipukhidiya iran ko Miyamara­tiyaya."
  85,8,"Na da-a ini kagowad iran kir­an a rowar sa Kapaparatiyaya a iran ko Allah, a Mabagur, a diyai­tan o Podi,"
  85,9,"So Khiruk ko Kapa-ar ko manga Langit a go so Lopa. Na so Allah i saksi ko langowan taman."
  85,10,"Mata-an! A siran a sominiksa ko Miyamaratiyaya , a manga Mama a go Miyamaratiyaya a man­ga Babai, oriyan niyan na da siran Thaobat, na bagiyan niran so siksa ko Naraka Jahannam, go bagiyan niran so siksa a Phakatotong."
  85,11,"Mata-an! A so siran a Miya­maratiyaya go Pinggalubuk iran so manga pipiya, na adun a bagiyan niran a manga Sorga a puphaman­gondas ko kababa-an niyan so man­ga lawasaig: Giyoto man so da-ag a mala."
  85,12,"Mata-an! A so siksa o Kad­ nan Ka na titho a mailot."
  85,13,"Mata-an! A Sukaniyan na Sukaniyan i Puphanagipo-on Man­gadun, go pupharoman Mangadun;"
  85,14,"Go Sukaniyan so Manapi, a Mala i Gagao,"
  85,15,"A Khiruk ko Aras, a Susula-an,"
  85,16,"A lnggogolalan Niyan so nganin a Kabaya lyan."
  85,17,"Ino a miyakatalingoma Ruka so Totholan ko manga tantara,-"
  85,18,"A so Pir-aon a go so pagtao a Samood?-"
  85,19,"Kuna, ka siran a da Pamar­atiyaya na shisi-i ko Kao ongkir!"
  85,20,"Na so Allah, na Katatangka­lan Niyan so mbalabala kiran!"
  85,21,"Kuna, ka Sukaniyan so Qur­-an a Susula-an,"
  85,22,"A madadalum ko lauh Mah­ fod."